<http://www.cgiraldolo.com/highrisk-meddev-&-invitrodev-diag> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This ontology semantically models the catalogue of high-risk medical devices and in-vitro diagnostic devices of the EUDAMED european database. It includes devices, manufacturers, identified risks, incidents and corrective safety actions."@en .
<http://www.cgiraldolo.com/highrisk-meddev-&-invitrodev-diag> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontology of the european catalogue of high-risk medical devices and in-vitro diagnostics devices."@en .
